Package game

Class Note

java.lang.Object
game.Note
All Implemented Interfaces:
MusicObject
public class Note
extends java.lang.Object
implements MusicObject
Overview - holds all info needed about a note - the data, the dimensions, the images of it, etc. UseCase - GameSession will compare user submitted notes, to the quiz's note, to determine if equal or not. Spawner will spawn or animate notes, by getting and manipulating its' internal nodes (image views, labels, or rectangles)
